      "title": "Four injured in motor accident on expressway",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four people have sustained injuries in a motor accident on the Central Expressway this morning (Aug 21).",
        "Among the injured is the well-known Advanced Level Examination tuition class instructor Dinesh Muthugala.",
        "However, none of them are in critical condition, according to the police."
